00:02:30.644 --> 00:02:31.425
di Internet!

00:02:31.449 --> 00:02:33.782
Rasanya seperti, saya akhirnya berhasil.

00:02:33.806 --> 00:02:35.108
Saya menekan "refresh."

00:02:35.132 --> 00:02:37.841
(Video) Komentar: Suaranya mengganggu.
